^ England, Paula (1993). "The Separative Self: Androcentric Bias in Neoclassical Assumptions", Beyond Economic Man: Feminist Theory and Economics, University of Chicago Press, pp. 37–53.
^ Ferber, M.A. and Julie A. Nelson, "Beyond Economic Man: Ten Years Later," in Marianne A. Ferber and Julie A. Nelson, eds., Feminist Economics Today: Beyond Economic Man. Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 2003.
^ Marilyn Waring (1988.) If Women Counted. San Francisco: Harper & Row. ISBN 0-06-250933-0
