^ Sutter, Daniel, and Rex Pjesky (2007). "Where Would Adam Smith Publish Today? The Near Absence of Math-free Research in Top Journals," Econ Journal Watch, 4(2), pp. 230–40. Abstract. Retrieved 2013-04-04.


